assignments.description:
(Nov 28: Normalized with other participation activities at 4 points. Grades scaled accordingly.)

Download and install Gephi: https://gephi.org/users/download/

Then download and import the airline dataset from http://gephi.org/datasets/airlines.gexf.zip

Visualize the airline graph with two graph layouts algorithms:

1. GeoLayout, for this you might need to install a plugin in Gephi

2. Any other layout of your choice

Encode some attribute(same or different) in these layouts. Feel free to use size and/or color channel on the nodes. Describe the encoding along with a data insight for each layout. 

Submit the description as pdf and SVG of the graph layout in a zipped file.
